# std.crypto.twofish
#
# Twofish block cipher implementation.
# Designed by Bruce Schneier as one of the AES finalists.
# Uses 128-bit blocks and 128/192/256-bit keys.
#
# NOTE: Native runtime implementation pending. Returns 0 (error)
# until the C runtime in zero_crypto.c is extended.
#

